      <div class="quotes__desc-section">
          
          <h2 class="quotes__title">What is MCP? </h2>
          <div class="quotes__separator"></div>
          <div class="quotes__desc text"><p>MCP stands for Model Context Protocol, an emerging open standard that enables AI models (like GPT, Claude, or Gemini) to securely and reliably interact with external tools, data sources, APIs, and user context in a structured way. It allows AI to operate with memory, relevance, and continuity—not in isolation, rather in sync with the enterprise context, user history, and operational intent. MCP makes AI infinitely useful in high-stakes, high-scale environments. </p>
</div>
